    <item>
      <title>特朗普的加密项目似乎在关税崩盘后购买了以太币</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/trump-s-crypto-project-appears-to-have-bought-ether-after-tariff-meltdown</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国总统短暂对墨西哥和加拿大征收关税，周末加密货币市场崩盘，与唐纳德·特朗普家族有关的去中心化金融项目世界自由金融 (World Liberty Financial) 似乎增持了价值数千万美元的以太币。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/trump-s-crypto-project-appears-to-have-bought-ether-after-tariff-meltdown</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 19:13:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
